en.answer_markdown:
## Viewing the available backups
The Backup page shows the existing snapshots and the main metadata useful for deciding which one to use.

### What to look at
- backup date and time;
- file size or weight;
- status or operational notes, if exposed;
- any signals about locks or ongoing processes.

### Why it matters
Reading the list carefully avoids downloading or restoring the wrong file, especially when several copies exist very close together in time.

fr.answer_markdown:
